eventData.messageText: At the foot of a mountain, in another world...
There is a small village.
There was a young boy who lived in that village.
This is the story of that young boy...
One morning...

■Young Boy■
"Yawn... The weather sure is nice today!"

■Young Boy■
"Ah!"

■Young Boy■
"Good morning, Mayor!"

■Mayor■
"Good morning. You came at a good time."

■Young Boy■
"A good time?"

■Mayor■
"Yes, 
actually the village has run out of medical herbs..."

■Mayor■
"I was hoping to ask you to go to town to buy some."

■Young Boy■
"I see. That's an easy task!"

■Mayor■
"Oh, thank you. Well, I'll leave it to you then."

■Young Boy■
"Okay!"

■Young Boy■
"The town! It's sure been a long time.
I want to look around since 
I have this chance."

■Young Boy■
"Well then, I should hurry along."

■Young Boy■
"Time to buy some herbs in town!"

And thus, the young boy was given
the task of herb shopping by the mayor.

In order to go to the town, 
the young boy first had to go through a forest.
A Meeting

■Young Boy■
"This forest sure is big..."

■Young Boy■
"I should have brought lunch.
I'm so hungry..."

■Young Boy■
"Hm?"

■Young Boy■
"Is that..."

■Young Boy■
"It's a monster!"

■Monster■
"Roaaaarr!"

■Young Boy■
"Okay... 
I've trained in the forest before."

■Young Boy■
"I should be able to take on 
something like this!"

■Young Boy■
"Hey-ya!"

■Monster■
"Graaah!"
The monster was defeated!

■Young Boy■
"I did it! I defeated the monster!"

■Young Boy■
"It was over pretty quickly, though..."

■Young Boy■
"I must have landed a critical hit
to defeat it in one attack."

■Young Boy■
"At this rate..."

■???■
"Wow, amazing! I saw that just now!"

■Young Girl■
"Sorry! I was just passing by!"

■Young Girl■
"I thought I heard a monster screaming,
so I came...and found you."

■Young Girl■
"That attack was amazing!"

■Young Boy■
"Really? Thanks."

■Young Boy■
"I'm glad you liked it."

■Young Girl■
"You're welcome."

■Young Girl■
"By the way..."

■Young Girl■
"What are you doing 
so deep in this forest?"

■Young Boy■
"Ah, actually, we need medicinal herbs.
I'm heading to the town to get them."

■Young Girl■
"Ah, me too! 
I'm just on my way to buy herbs there."

■Young Girl■
"Despite my looks, 
I'm an herbalist and magician."

■Young Girl■
"Let's go to town together! 
You don't mind, do you?"

■Young Boy■
"Okay, sure.
I could use some magical support."

■Young Boy■
"Let's go! Leave the fighting to me."

■Young Girl■
"Sure! And I'll handle magic and healing."
And so the two headed to the town together.

■Young Girl■
"We're here!"

■Young Girl■
"We're finally in town!"

■Young Boy■
(I'm... beat...)

■Young Girl■
"Huh? You look weak. Are you okay?"

■Young Boy■
"I'm fine, I'm fine!"

■Young Girl■
"Ah, that's the herb shopkeeper!"

■Young Boy■
"Ah, perfect."

■Young Boy■
"Let's go buy the herbs."

■Young Boy■
"This is a problem."

■Young Boy■
"Because of all the monsters,
they can't restock herbs..."

■Young Girl■
"I do know where
the herbs grow naturally."

■Young Girl■
"However,
with all the monsters around, 
it might be too much..."

■Young Girl■
"Ah!"

■Young Girl■
"But if you're with me, 
it should be possible!"

■Young Boy■
"Should be... you say?"

■Young Girl■
"Definitely possible!"

■Young Girl■
"Magic and brawn. We're perfect together."

■Young Boy■
"Yeah..."

■Young Boy■
"Okay. I can't go back empty-handed."

■Young Boy■
"Let's take some monsters down, 
get the herbs, and get away."

■Young Girl■
"I'm glad to hear you say that!"

■Young Girl■
"Monsters are scary, but... 
I'll do what I can!"
And so, the two headed off to obtain the herbs.

While continuing to defeat hoards of monsters,
they headed to the where the herbs grew...

■Young Boy■
"Hey-ya!"

■Monster■
"Hiss..."
The monster was defeated!

■Young Boy■
"Phew..."

■Young Girl■
"Good job! 
We're almost at 
the place where the herbs grow."

■Young Boy■
"I see...
Anyway, 
do these monsters feel extra tough to you?"

■Young Girl■
"That's what I sensed...
There's more magic than before."

■Young Boy■
"Yeah. We'd better be ready."

■Young Girl■
"I agree."

■Young Girl■
"Ah, but..."

■Young Girl■
"You look so awesome when you're fighting!"

■Young Boy■
"What?! Really?"

■Young Girl■
"Yeah!"

■Young Girl■
"It's just so amazing 
how you take down those monsters!"

■Young Boy■
"Thanks. 
But it's all thanks to 
you helping with magic."

■Young Girl■
"Oh really? 
Well, flattery will get you nowhere!"

■Young Boy■
"But..."

■Young Boy■
"The terrain seems like the road to town,
yet the monsters seem stronger."

■Young Boy■
"It might be connected to their numbers, 
too."

■Young Girl■
"That's true."

■Young Girl■
"I just wish that taking them down
would reduce their numbers, really."

■Young Girl■
"Now that you mention it, I feel like
there were reports of monster swarms 
somewhere, before..."

■Young Boy■
"Really?"

■Young Girl■
"Yeah. It's common, recently."

■Monster■
"Grrr..."

■Young Girl■
"A monster?! But we're almost there!"

■Young Boy■
"Only a little more to go! Let's do this."

■Young Girl■
"Yeah!"

And so, the two headed to where the herb grows,
fighting monsters along the way.

■Young Girl■
"Whoa!"

■Young Girl■
"There are so many gene herbs! Wow!"

■Young Boy■
"So these are gene herbs..."

Although they struggled against the monsters,
they finally made it to where the herb grows.

■Young Girl■
"There are so many! 
It was definitely worth coming here!"

■Young Girl■
"Let's pick them and hurry back!"

■Young Boy■
"Yeah."
*Thud...*
*thud*

■Young Girl■
"I'm getting a bad feeling."

■Young Boy■
"Me too..."
*THUD!*

■Giant Monster■
"Roaaaarrrr!"

■Young Girl■
"Eeek, there it is!"

■Young Boy■
"Oh, no... Is this the end?"

■Young Girl■
"Hey! Fight!"

■Young Boy■
"Okay... I'll try."
A boss monster has appeared!

The two put a stop to the large hoards of monsters 
and restored herb distribution.

Ready to go back to their own villages, 
the two prepared to leave.

■Young Girl■
"Whew...
That was crazy!"

■Young Boy■
"It was. I really leveled up a bunch..."

■Young Girl■
"Me too, me too! 
I might be the highest level in my village!"

■Young Boy■
"There sure have been a lot of these 
mass monster sightings lately..."

■Young Boy■
"I heard some rumors in town."

■Young Boy■
"This power should come in handy 
if something happens again, but..."

■Young Girl■
"Yeah. 
And I'll work on my herbalism skills!"

■Young Girl■
"My dream is 
to be the best herbalist in the land!"

■Young Boy■
"I could see that! That's great."

■Young Boy■
"You really supported me there.
I'm sure you'll be a great herbalist."

■Young Girl■
"Thanks! I definitely will!"

■Young Girl■
"Leveling up from this fight is 
just the first step towards my dream!"

■Young Girl■
"The town herbalist even remembers me now.
My business might take off!"

■Young Boy■
"You sure have it together."

■Young Boy■
"Honestly, I don't even have a dream..."

■Young Girl■
"Really?"

■Young Girl■
"That a bit surprising!"

■Young Boy■
"Surprising?"

■Young Girl■
"Yeah! You're good at fighting. 
Now that this is done,"

■Young Girl■
"I figured you'd go adventuring 
and solve problems."

■Young Boy■
"Huh... An adventure."

■Young Boy■
"Now that you mention it,
that sort of thing was popular 
a while back."

■Young Girl■
"Yeah! So that's what I figured you'd do."

■Young Girl■
"Large monsters gather underlings
and cause problems for people. 
Like this time."

■Young Girl■
"In fact, 
there were so many adventurers before
that we never saw monsters like this."

■Young Girl■
"That's what the rumors say."

■Young Boy■
"I see..."

■Young Boy■
"If that's true,
then that sounds like a real problem."

■Young Girl■
"Yeah."

■Young Girl■
"Ah, if you do go on an adventure,
be sure to let me join your party!"

■Young Girl■
"They just sound so cool, after all."

■Young Boy■
"There's a lot you want to do."

■Young Boy■
"Anyway... An adventure might be nice."

■Young Boy■
"Ah..."

■Young Girl■
"Oh... This is where we part ways."

■Young Girl■
"Your village is that way, 
and mine is this way..."

■Young Boy■
"Yeah..."

■Young Girl■
"Hehe, 
I'll be sure to visit your village soon!"

■Young Boy■
"Ah, thanks! 
And I'll probably go see you, too."

■Young Girl■
"Alright! I'm looking forward to it."

■Young Girl■
"Thank you so much for today!"

■Young Boy■
"Of course!"

■Young Girl■
"Ehehe, see you later!"

■Young Boy■
"Yeah, later!"
And so, the two returned to their villages.

Their little adventure had ended,
but neither knew that a larger adventure was 
yet to come.
